                    <p><strong>August 27th, 2021</strong></p>

                    <h5>Haldi <span class="time">10AM-11AM</span></h5>
                    <p>For the haldi ceremony, everyone gets to "paint" the bride and groom with a <b>turmeric
                            (haldi)</b> paste.
                        The Haldi ceremony is a ritual holy bath also known as pithi ceremony, which is one of the
                        pre-wedding
                        ceremonies in India. Turmeric, oil and water are applied to both the bride and groom
                        by married
                        women on the morning of the wedding. The mixture is believed to bless the couple before the
                        wedding.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-6 col-md-4 rightcol">
